fields.name: Scheduler
fields.description: IPVS scheduler, for more information please see http://www.linuxvirtualserver.org/docs/scheduling.html.

fields.name: TcpFinTimeoutSeconds
fields.description: The timeout value used for IPVS TCP sessions after receiving a FIN in seconds. Must be a positive integer value.

fields.name: TcpTimeoutSeconds
fields.description: The timeout value used for idle IPVS TCP sessions in seconds. Must be a positive integer value.

fields.name: UdpTimeoutSeconds
fields.description: The timeout value used for IPVS UDP packets in seconds. Must be a positive integer value.
